import React from "react"

    CardTitle,
    Label,
    FormGroup,
    Form,
    Input,
    InputGroupAddon,
    InputGroupText,
    InputGroup,
    Container,
    Row,
    Col
  } from "reactstrap";

function Main() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <Col>
                    <FormGroup check className="text-left">
                        <Label check>
                            <Input type="checkbox" />
                            <span className="form-check-sign" />I agree to the{" "}terms and conditions.

                            <Input type="checkbox" />
                            <span className="form-check-sign" />I agree to the{" "}terms and conditions.

                            <Input type="checkbox" />
                            <span className="form-check-sign" />I agree to the{" "}terms and conditions.

                            <Input type="checkbox" />
                            <span className="form-check-sign" />I agree to the{" "}terms and conditions.
                        </Label>
                    </FormGroup>
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Main
